  "text": "We used the HaloTag technology and immunocytochemistry to also show that the β1Int-HaloTag protein co-localized with expected membrane proteins, such as cadherin and transferrin receptors [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . To assess protein colocalization at the membrane, live cells expressing β1Int-Targeting HaloTag protein to the cell surface HaloTag were labeled with the HaloTag 488 ligand, and then processed for immunocytochemistry ( Figure 4b ).",
